@startuml
autonumber

queue "RabbitMQ DLQ" as MQ_DLQ
participant "DLQ Consumer (Alert Service)" as DLQ_Consumer
participant "Telegram Bot API" as TeleBot
actor "Developer Group (Telegram)" as Developer

group #FFF0F5 Xử lý DLQ & Cảnh báo Telegram
    note over MQ_DLQ, Developer: Xử lý DLQ & Cảnh báo Telegram
    MQ_DLQ -> DLQ_Consumer: Nhận tin nhắn lỗi từ DLQ
    DLQ_Consumer -> DLQ_Consumer: Parse payload & Trích xuất nguyên nhân lỗi (Error stack)
    DLQ_Consumer -> TeleBot ++: POST /sendMessage (Chat ID, Markdown format)
    TeleBot --> DLQ_Consumer --: 200 OK
    TeleBot -> Developer: Hiển thị cảnh báo đỏ 🚨 (Kèm payload, Stacktrace)
end
@enduml